txt.en: Defeat two hundred and fifty monsters in one Skirmish session
You have returned several of the risen Dead in the Barrow-downs to their proper resting places and banished the fell spirits which disturbed them.
You have returned many of the risen Dead in the Barrow-downs to their proper resting places and banished the fell spirits which disturbed them.

The Barrow-downs were once a stronghold of the Rangers of Cardolan, but after the destruction of the last remnant of Cardolan, the Witch-king sent fell spirits to stir the bones of the dead and make it a place of terror.
